        <!-- Q1 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设 <m>f(x) \in C[0, a], f(x) \in D(0, a)</m>, 且 <m>f(a)=0</m>, 证明: <m>\exists \xi \in(0,1) </m>, s.t  <m>2 f(\xi)+\xi f^{\prime}(\xi)=0</m>.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证: 令 <m>F(x)=x^{2} f(x)</m>, <m>\because f(x) \in C[0, a], f(x) \in D(0, a)</m></p>

                    <p><m>\because f(x) \in C[0, a], f(x) \in D(0, a)</m> 
                    <m>\therefore F(x) \in C[0, a], F(x) \in D(0, a)</m></p>

                    <p>又  <m>\because F(0)=0, F(a)=0</m>, <m>\therefore F(x)</m> 在 <m>[0, a]</m> 上满足罗尔定理.
                    即 <m>\exists \xi \in(0, a)</m> 使得 <m>F^{\prime}(\xi)=0</m>. 
                    即 <m>2 \xi f(\xi)+\xi^{2} f^{\prime}(\xi)=0</m>. 即 <m>2 f(\xi)+\xi f^{\prime}(\xi)=0</m>.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q2 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设 <m>f(x) \in C[a, b], f(x) \in D(a, b)</m>, 且 <m>f(a)=f(b)=0</m>, 证明: <m>\exists \xi \in(0,1)</m>, s.t <m>\lambda f(\xi)+f^{\prime}(\xi)=0</m>.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证: 令 <m>F(x)=e^{\lambda x} f(x)</m>, <m>\because f(x) \in C[a, b], f(x) \in D(a, b)</m>
                    <m>\therefore F(x) \in C[a, b], F(x) \in D(a, b)</m></p>

                    <p>又 <m>\because F(a)=e^{\lambda a} f(a)=0, F(b)=e^{\lambda b} f(b)=0</m></p>

                    <p><m>\therefore F(x)</m> 在 <m>[a, b]</m> 上满足罗尔定理. 即 <m>\exists \xi \in(0,1)</m> 使得 <m>\mathrm{F}^{\prime}(\xi)=0</m>.
                    即 <m>e^{\lambda \xi} f^{\prime}(\xi)+\lambda e^{\lambda \xi} f(\xi)=0</m>. 消去 <m>e^{\lambda \xi}</m>, 即 <m>f^{\prime}(\xi)+\lambda f(\xi)=0</m>.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q3 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设 <m>f(x), g(x)</m> 在 <m>[a, b]</m> 上连续, 在 <m>(a, b)</m> 内可导, 且 <m>g(x) \neq 0</m>, <m>f(a) g(b)=g(a) f(b)</m>, 试证 <m>\exists \xi \in(a, b)</m>, 使得 <m>f^{\prime}(\xi) g(\xi)=f(\xi) g^{\prime}(\xi)</m>.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证: <m>\because f^{\prime}(\xi) g(\xi)=f(\xi) g^{\prime}(\xi) \Leftrightarrow f^{\prime}(\xi) g(\xi)-f(\xi) g^{\prime}(\xi)=0</m>, 又 <m>g(\xi) \neq 0, \Rightarrow \frac{f^{\prime}(\xi) g(\xi)-f(\xi) g^{\prime}(\xi)}{g^{2}(\xi)}=\left[\frac{f(x)}{g(x)}\right]_{x=\xi}^{\prime}=0</m>,</p>

                    <p><m>\therefore</m> 令 <m>\varphi(x)=\frac{f(x)}{g(x)}</m>.</p>

                    <p>由题设知 <m>\varphi(x)</m> 在 <m>[a, b]</m> 上连续, 在 <m>(a, b)</m> 可导 :
                    <me>
                    \varphi^{\prime}(x)=\frac{f^{\prime}(x) g(x)-f(x) g^{\prime}(x)}{g^{2}(x)},
                    </me></p>

                    <p>且 <m>\varphi(a)=\frac{f(a)}{g(a)}=\frac{f(b)}{g(b)}=\varphi(b) </m>, 故由 Rolle 定理知 <m>\exists \xi \in(a, b)</m>, 使得 <m>\varphi^{\prime}(\xi)=0</m>, 即 <m>f^{\prime}(\xi) g(\xi)=f(\xi) g^{\prime}(\xi)</m>.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q4 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设 <m>f(x)</m> 在 <m>[a, b]</m> 上连续, 在 <m>(a, b)</m> 内二阶可导, 联接 <m>(a, f(a)),(b, f(b))</m> 直线交于曲线 <m>y=f(x)</m> 于 <m>(c, f(c)), a \lt c \lt b</m>, 求证: <m>\exists \xi \in(a, b)</m>, 使得 <m>f^{\prime \prime}(\xi)=0</m>.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证明: <m>f(x)</m> 在 <m>[a, c],[c, b]</m> 上满足拉格朗日中值定理条件,则
                    <me>
                    f^{\prime}\left(\xi_{1}\right)=\frac{f(c)-f(a)}{c-a}\left(a \lt \xi_{1} \lt c\right), \quad f^{\prime}\left(\xi_{2}\right)=\frac{f(b)-f(c)}{b-c}\left(c \lt \xi_{2} \lt b\right)
                    </me></p>

                    <p>由于 <m>A(a, f(a)), B(b, f(b)), C(c, f(c))</m> 三点共线, 则有
                    <me>
                    \frac{f(c)-f(a)}{c-a}=\frac{f(b)-f(c)}{b-c}=\frac{f(b)-f(a)}{b-a}=K_{A B}\left(K_{A B} \text { 为 } A B \text { 的斜率 }\right)
                    </me></p>

                    <p>再对 <m>f^{\prime}(x)</m> 在 <m>\left[\xi_{1}, \xi_{2}\right]</m> 上应用罗尔定理得 <m>f^{\prime \prime}(\xi)=0, \xi \in\left(\xi_{1}, \xi_{2}\right) \subset(a, b)</m>.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q5 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设 <m>f(x)</m> 在 <m>[a, b]</m> 上连续, 在 <m>(a, b)</m> 内可导, 且 <m>f^{\prime}(x) \neq 0</m>, 试证: 存在 <m>\xi, \eta \in(a, b)</m> 使得 <m>\frac{f^{\prime}(\xi)}{f^{\prime}(\eta)}=\frac{\mathrm{e}^{b}-\mathrm{e}^{a}}{b-a} \mathrm{e}^{-\eta}</m>.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证: 注意到要证的等式中, 除了有函数 <m>f(x)</m> 外, 还涉及到函数 <m>\mathrm{e}^{x}</m>, 这就要考虑使用Cauchy定理.</p>

                <p>因为 <m>f(x), \mathrm{e}^{x}</m> 在 <m>[a, b]</m> 满足 Cauchy 定理的条件, 于是有</p>

                <p><me>\frac{\mathrm{e}^{b}-\mathrm{e}^{a}}{f(b)-f(a)}=\frac{\mathrm{e}^{\eta}}{f^{\prime}(\eta)}, \text{其中} \eta \in(a, b)\quad (1)</me></p>

                <p>又在 <m>[a, b]</m> 上对 <m>f(x)</m> 使用 Lagrange 定理, 得</p>

                <p><me>f(b)-f(a)=(b-a) f^{\prime}(\xi), \text{其中} \xi \in(a, b)\quad (2)</me></p>

                <p>将(2)式代入(1)式, 得 <m>\frac{\mathrm{e}^{b}-\mathrm{e}^{a}}{(b-a) f^{\prime}(\xi)}=\frac{\mathrm{e}^{\eta}}{f^{\prime}(\eta)}</m>, 即 <m>\frac{f^{\prime}(\xi)}{f^{\prime}(\eta)}=\frac{\mathrm{e}^{b}-\mathrm{e}^{a}}{b-a} \mathrm{e}^{-\eta} \quad(\xi, \eta \in(a, b))</m>.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q6 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设 <m>f(x)</m> 在 <m>[0,1]</m> 上连续, 在 <m>(0,1)</m> 内可导, 且 <m>f(0)=0, f(1)=\frac{1}{3}</m>,试证 <m>\exists \xi \in\left(0, \frac{1}{2}\right), \eta \in\left(\frac{1}{2}, 1\right)</m> 使得 <m>f^{\prime}(\xi)+f^{\prime}(\eta)=\xi^{2}+\eta^{2}</m>.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证 <m>\because f^{\prime}(\xi)+f^{\prime}(\eta)=\xi^{2}+\eta^{2} \Leftrightarrow\left[f^{\prime}(\xi)-\xi^{2}\right]+\left[f^{\prime}(\eta)-\eta^{2}\right]=0</m>,而 <m>f^{\prime}(\xi)-\xi^{2}=\left[f(x)-\frac{1}{3} x^{3}\right]_{x=\xi}^{\prime}</m>, <m>\therefore</m> 令 <m>\varphi(x)=f(x)-\frac{x^{3}}{3}</m>.  <m>\varphi(0)=\varphi(1)=0</m>.</p>

                    <p>由题设知 <m>\varphi(x)</m> 在 <m>\left[0, \frac{1}{2}\right]</m> 与 <m>\left[\frac{1}{2}, 1\right]</m> 上满足Lagrange定理条件,故 <m>\exists \xi \in\left(0, \frac{1}{2}\right), \eta \in\left(\frac{1}{2}, 1\right)</m>, 使得
                    <me>
                    \begin{array}{l}
                    \varphi\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)-\varphi(0)=\left(\frac{1}{2}-0\right) \varphi^{\prime}(\xi)=\frac{1}{2}\left[f^{\prime}(\xi)-\xi^{2}\right], \\
                    \varphi(1)-\varphi\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)=\left(1-\frac{1}{2}\right) \varphi^{\prime}(\eta)=\frac{1}{2}\left[f^{\prime}(\eta)-\eta^{2}\right] .
                    \end{array}
                    </me></p>

                    <p>二式相加得 <m>\varphi(1)-\varphi(0)=\frac{1}{2}\left[f^{\prime}(\xi)-\xi^{2}\right]+\frac{1}{2}\left[f^{\prime}(\eta)-\eta^{2}\right]=0</m>,即 <m>f^{\prime}(\xi)+f^{\prime}(\eta)=\xi^{2}+\eta^{2}</m>.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q7 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设 <m>f \in \mathrm{C}[a, b]</m>, <m>f \in \mathrm{D}(a, b), 0 \lt a \lt b</m>. 证明 <m>\exists \xi, \eta \in(a, b)</m>, 使得
                <me>
                f^{\prime}(\xi)=\left(a^{2}+a b+b^{2}\right) \frac{f^{\prime}(\eta)}{3 \eta^{2}} 
                </me>
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证: 由Lagrange定理, <m>\exists \xi \in(a, b)</m> 使得
                    <me>
                    f^{\prime}(\xi)=\frac{f(b)-f(a)}{b-a} .\quad(1)
                    </me></p>

                    <p>设 <m>g(x)=x^{3}</m>, 则 <m>f(x), g(x)</m> 在 <m>[a, b]</m> 上满足Cauchy定理条件, <m>\therefore \exists \eta \in(a, b)</m>, 使得 <m>\frac{f(b)-f(a)}{b^{3}-a^{3}}=\frac{f^{\prime}(\eta)}{3 \eta^{2}}</m>,即. 
                    <me> \frac{f(b)-f(a)}{b-a}=\left(a^{2}+a b+b^{2}\right) \frac{f^{\prime}(\eta)}{3 \eta^{2}} \quad(2)</me>
                    由(1), (2) 即得 <m>f^{\prime}(\xi)=\left(a^{2}+a b+b^{2}\right) \frac{f^{\prime}(\eta)}{3 \eta^{2}}</m>.</p>

                    <p>下列几种情况可考虑这样作辅助函数：
                    <me>
                    \begin{array}{|c|c|}
                    \hline 要证式子中含  &amp;  作辅助函数 \\
                    \hline f(\xi)+\xi f^{\prime}(\xi)   &amp;   \varphi(x)=x f(x)  \\
                    \hline \xi f^{\prime}(\xi)-f(\xi)   &amp;   \varphi(x)=\frac{f(x)}{x}  \\
                    \hline \xi f^{\prime}(\xi)-n f(\xi)   &amp;   \varphi(x)=\frac{f(x)}{x^{n}}  \\
                    \hline \lambda f(\xi)+f^{\prime}(\xi)   &amp;   \varphi(x)=\mathrm{e}^{\lambda x} f(x)  \\
                    \hline g^{\prime}(\xi) f(\xi)+f^{\prime}(\xi)   &amp;  \varphi(x)=\mathrm{e}^{g(x)} f(x)  \\
                    \hline g(a, b)(\text { 如 }\int_{a}^{b} f(x) \mathrm{d} x )   &amp;   \varphi(x)=g(a, x), x \in[a, b]  \\
                    \hline
                    \end{array}
                    </me>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q8 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设 <m>f(x)</m> 在 <m>[0,1]</m> 上连续, <m>f(x)</m> 在 <m>(0,1)</m> 内可导, 且 <m>f(0)=0, f(1)=1</m>, 证明: (1) <m>\exists x_{0} \in(0,1)</m> 使得 <m>f\left(x_{0}\right)=2-3 x_{0}</m> ;(2) <m>\exists \xi, \eta \in(0,1), \xi \neq \eta</m> 使得 <m>\left[1+f^{\prime}(\xi)\right]\left[1+f^{\prime}(\eta)\right]=4</m>.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证明: (1) 令 <m>F(x)=f(x)-2+3 x</m>,  <m>F(x)</m> 在 <m>[0,1]</m> 上连续, 且 <m>F(0)=-2, F(1)=2 </m>
                由介值定理, 存在 <m> x_{0} \in(0,1) </m> 使得 <m> F\left(x_{0}\right)=0 </m> 即 <m> f\left(x_{0}\right)=2-3 x_{0} </m>
                (2) <m> F(x) </m> 分别在 <m> \left[0, x_{0}\right],\left[x_{0}, 1\right] </m> 上利用拉格朗日中值定理
                <me>
                \begin{array}{rl}
                \frac{2}{x_{0}}  =\frac{F\left(x_{0}\right)-F(0)}{x_{0}}=F^{\prime}(\xi)=f^{\prime}(\xi)+3  &amp;  0 \lt \xi \lt x_{0} \\
                \frac{2}{1-x_{0}}  =\frac{F(1)-F\left(x_{0}\right)}{1-x_{0}}=F^{\prime}(\eta)=f^{\prime}(\eta)+3  &amp;  x_{0} \lt \eta \lt 1
                \end{array}
                </me></p>

                <p>两式都减 <m>2</m> ,后相乘
                <me>
                \left[1+f^{\prime}(\xi)\right]\left[1+f^{\prime}(\eta)\right]=\frac{2-2 x_{0}}{x_{0}} \cdot \frac{2 x_{0}}{1-x_{0}}=4
                </me>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q9 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
