                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解 <m>\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 1} \frac{x^{3}-3 x+2}{x^{3}-x^{2}-x+1} \xlongequal{\frac{0}{0}} \lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 1} \frac{3 x^{2}-3}{3 x^{2}-2 x-1} \xlongequal{\frac{0}{0}} \lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 1} \frac{6 x}{6 x-2}=\frac{3}{2} </m>.
