        <!-- Q11 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    极限 <m>\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{(x-\sin x) e^{-x^{2}}}{\sqrt{1-x^{3}}-1} =\underline{} </m>
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解: 分母等价代换/分子上极限非零的因子先求</p>

                <p><me>\begin{aligned}
                    \lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{(x-\sin x) e^{-x^{2}}}{\sqrt{1-x^{3}}-1} &amp; =\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{x-\sin x}{-\frac{x^{3}}{2}}\\
                &amp; =-2 \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{x-\sin x}{x^{3}} \stackrel{\frac{0}{0}}{=}-2 \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{1-\cos x}{3 x^{2}}\\ &amp; =-2 \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\frac{x^{2}}{2}}{3 x^{2}}=\frac{-1}{3}
                \end{aligned}
                </me>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q12 -->
        <exercise>
