                    解: <m>\because \forall a \in \mathbf{R}, \lim\limits _{x \rightarrow a^{ \pm}} y \neq \infty</m>, 故 <m>4</m> 条曲线均无垂直渐近线.
                    对于(A), <m>\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow \infty} \frac{y}{x}=\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow \infty}\left(1+\frac{\sin x}{x}\right)=1</m> (存在), 但 <m>\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow \infty}(y-1 \cdot x)=\lim _{x \rightarrow \infty} \sin x</m> 不存在, 故无渐近线.
                    对于(B), <m>\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow \infty} \frac{y}{x}=\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow \infty}\left(x+\frac{\sin x}{x}\right)=\infty</m> (不存在),对于(D)同理知其无渐近线.</p>

                    <p>选C.</p>

                    <p>事实上, 对于  (C), <m>\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow \infty} \frac{y}{x}=\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow \infty}\left(1+\frac{1}{x} \sin \frac{1}{x}\right)=1</m>, 且 <m>\lim \limits_{x \rightarrow \infty}(y-1 \cdot x)=\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow \infty} \sin \frac{1}{x}=0</m>, 故 <m>y=x</m> 是其渐近线.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>


